{"tid":1839881,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"求救 天竺鼠打交","createTime":"2020-01-24T15:32:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-06T05:26:54.000Z","uid":261290,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"1e3b4ab28ea1b257667a34b359ca467070918bf8","tid":1839881,"uid":261290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T15:32:38.000Z","msg":"我前日買左一隻，琴日再買多左一隻，將新果隻放落去之後，舊果隻就成日追住佢屎忽，新果隻就好驚係度叫又跑走，然後舊果隻就一直追。<br />\n<br />\n到今朝見到新果隻耳仔損左少少，似比舊果隻打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AiKNnw8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAiKNnw8.png&h=b5f889f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我今日將個籠用滴露洗一次，洗走哂佢地啲味等佢地重新分地盤。點知新果隻都係被打又唔反抗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我上網有睇過話係頭幾日都會持續追打下，要分到階級之後就唔會再打，以後融洽相處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好想問有無養過養緊既人可以幫下手，到底係空間唔夠所以打，定真係唔夾？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n補充：兩隻都係女，明明上網睇過女女正常都唔會打"},{"pid":"d58108837764c4fb19878a4cf32408c9b6184116","tid":1839881,"uid":162008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T15:33:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要話俾醫護知，無論你地決定係點，市民會支持你地</span></span><br />\n<br />\n原Post<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">大家支唔支持醫護大罷工？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">入黎幫手推十次</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1837575\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1837575</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"12d1e25ead328c5598c239fe1d4b648f669cdc41","tid":1839881,"uid":95560,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T16:57:27.000Z","msg":"你唔知要分開籠養㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cb29bff2c8a23a95ac69788acab99825f1930c8","tid":1839881,"uid":165336,"like":4,"dislike":7,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T17:01:06.000Z","msg":"你都戇鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />鼠本來就唔係群居動物"},{"pid":"92847d84fd3aaef1ce0f334aaccea3080e40b1c7","tid":1839881,"uid":215026,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"12d1e25ead328c5598c239fe1d4b648f669cdc41","tid":1839881,"uid":95560,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T16:57:27.000Z","msg":"你唔知要分開籠養㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T17:24:04.000Z","msg":"倉鼠就係<br />\n天竺鼠係群居動物<br />\n<br />\nBtw樓主係咪一隻大一隻細"},{"pid":"0dd53559c4e91947ca8067d3e2a80393796939bf","tid":1839881,"uid":134325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T18:06:33.000Z","msg":"有無用神仙水幫佢噴少少喺傷口？"},{"pid":"3990f473f87539f0f7104256691d9dba884871cc","tid":1839881,"uid":2475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T18:09:16.000Z","msg":"這樣下去不行<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82b6077ad217cbb28a3f16fa0c1c6fc4c5acfa89","tid":1839881,"uid":221635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T18:33:32.000Z","msg":"我個隻都不斷吹人⋯<br />\n所以唯有分籠養<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9a48b41aa7e90bf7b42395aef2dd69edd7ff866","tid":1839881,"uid":261290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"92847d84fd3aaef1ce0f334aaccea3080e40b1c7","tid":1839881,"uid":215026,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"12d1e25ead328c5598c239fe1d4b648f669cdc